# HeapVortex - Main Application Component

## Overview

This file serves as the main entry point of the **HeapVortex** application. It combines a real-time 3D heap visualization with an interactive telemetry dashboard, providing users with an immersive JVM memory profiling experience.

The application is built using **React**, **TypeScript**, **React Three Fiber**, **Three.js**, and **Tailwind CSS** to create a modern and responsive interface.

---

## Features

- Full-screen interactive 3D visualization
- Real-time heap object rendering
- Orbit camera controls for navigation
- Dynamic star-field background
- Realistic lighting effects
- Live telemetry sidebar
- JVM connection status indicator
- Bottom HUD displaying heap statistics
- Loading indicator while 3D assets initialize
- Responsive overlay UI using Tailwind CSS

---

